Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作做完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你妈妈如此优秀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 看我把小翔战翻
